Subject: CHEBI:70758
Value: UDP-N-acetylmuramoyl-L-alanyl-gamma-D-glutamyl-L-lysyl-D-alanyl-D-alaninate(3-) in which the anomeric centre of the pyranose fragment has alpha-configuration.

Subject: CHEBI:101096
Value: 1,3-Benzothiazole substituted a sulfonamide and an ethoxy group at positions 2 and 6, respectively. A carbonic anhydrase inhibitor, it has been used in the treatment of glaucoma, and as a diuretic.
